covered: Valid Request: Scenarios @TC01, @TC02, @TC03, @TC04, @TC05, @TC06, @TC07, @TC08, @TC09, @TC13, @TC14, @TC18, @TC19, @TC20, @TC21, @TC23, @TC24, @TC27 cover successful retrieval with various parameters and conditions.
Empty Response: @TC06 and @TC24 handle cases with no matching data.

Query Parameters: Multiple scenarios (@TC02, @TC03, @TC04, @TC05, @TC08, @TC09, @TC10, @TC11, @TC12, @TC13, @TC14, @TC18, @TC19, @TC20, @TC21, @TC23, @TC24, @TC27) test different combinations and invalid values.
Error Handling: @TC09, @TC10, @TC11, @TC12, @TC13, @TC14, @TC15, @TC16, @TC17, @TC25 cover various error scenarios including invalid inputs, server errors, and service unavailability.
Authentication: @TC13 and @TC14 test missing and invalid tokens.
gaps: Pagination: No explicit tests for handling large datasets with pagination beyond basic offset/limit, especially for very large numbers.
Caching Behavior: No tests verify cache headers like ETag or Cache-Control.
Rate Limiting: No scenarios test system behavior under high request volume or throttling.
Concurrent Requests: No tests for simultaneous requests to verify consistency and performance under load.
Regression/Backward Compatibility: Limited coverage for previously supported parameter combinations beyond @TC21.
Accessibility: No tests for UI or accessibility features.
Timeouts and performance under load: Only @TC19 hints at performance, but no explicit timeout or stress tests.
recommendations: Add explicit tests for pagination with very large datasets to verify correct handling of offset and limit boundaries.
Include tests to verify caching headers like ETag and Cache-Control for cache validation.
Implement rate limiting and throttling tests to ensure system stability under high load.
Create concurrency tests to check for data consistency during simultaneous requests.
Expand regression testing to cover all previous parameter combinations and behaviors.
Add accessibility and UI-related tests if applicable.
Include performance and timeout tests to validate system responsiveness under stress.
